description: David Masters is a young doctor with an unusual penchant for danger! When someone's in peril, Young Dr. Masters is on the scene and ready to save lives! But his real passion lies with medical research, finding out the cures for deadly diseases. Can he balance his responsibilities as a doctor and a scientist while his father tries to control his fate?

description: The veteran captain Ivvro has been recruited once more, to command a convicts' squadron, in the long war against the black elfs. During the battle a mysterious fog transports them to a strange land, where they will have to fight another war, this time, to survive.
